{"tid":622804,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"喺公廁俾我捉到個死𡃁仔痾尿唔沖廁，我捉住佢鬧咗佢一餐","createTime":"2018-04-09T12:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T10:49:04.000Z","uid":157510,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7deadcef09bc173943612a7673479223cb605c31","tid":622804,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"話說頭先屎急我去咗公廁爆石<br />\n<br />\n點知一痾完出廁格就見到有個死𡃁仔唔 閂門唔揭起廁所板就咁痾尿落去個屎塔到<br />\n<br />\n污糟唔再講，佢竟然連如廁沖水都skip埋<br />\n<br />\n有無搞撚錯<br />\n<br />\n我即刻興過火屎，一招擒拿手的起個細路大喝一聲<br />\n<br />\n&quot;痾完尿唔識沖廁呀?有無公民意識呀?信唔信阿叔帶你過隔離食返我頭先痾嗰篤屎?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n個細路一聽到就即刻嚇到咸咗，流住馬尿咁沖返自己篤尿<br />\n<br />\n相信個細路受過依次教訓之後，以後都會記得痾完尿要沖廁，依個世界亦少一個無公德心既人<br />\n<br />\n嘻，我又做咗件好事了!"},{"pid":"30da31d7b23dbc6640bc84896fdfc8f6d7ebcfec","tid":622804,"uid":8572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"5b8b12b2da7a58717d2cba1dd1e22eb0227ef546","tid":622804,"uid":157000,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"唔知點解啲人去公廁真係唔鐘意沖廁, 拉一拉手制好難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由老到嫩都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405666c07e95b6f7b04b6ed1fa23a2e61f0c9214","tid":622804,"uid":157510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b8b12b2da7a58717d2cba1dd1e22eb0227ef546","tid":622804,"uid":157000,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"唔知點解啲人去公廁真係唔鐘意沖廁, 拉一拉手制好難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由老到嫩都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"38d24f6d59b1c041f73f58db93c5f7e28c48f38c","tid":622804,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c